{"tid":203060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何沛謙：港視不獲牌無理據","createTime":"2017-04-16T04:23:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T05:00:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5398862f03c4ed975e95eed66572b9a7b7bdeb6f","tid":203060,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:23:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991696&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991696%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&d=Ii3GHnPqKzd0SLaHQS96CL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=37535358\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19991696%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170416&h=bdb0b2ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19991696&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170416</a><br />\n<br />\n何沛謙：港視不獲牌無理據<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港電視因「一男子」因素不獲發免費電視牌照。事隔3年半，上月卸任通訊事務管理局主席的資深大律師何沛謙（圖），昨在港台節目《香港家書》重提「憾事」，指當時3間申請牌照的電視台中，港視表現最進取卻唯一落選，公眾看不到政府有何實質理據，令他更感失望，「喺呢件事上面，我唔覺得最終市民大眾係得到一個滿意解釋」。<br />\n何沛謙於2008年起出任通訊局主席，他在《香港家書》指出，當時上任期望讓公眾看到局方「好公平、公正處理問題」。他指早於2009、2010年時，已聽見不少聲音指免費電視節目選擇少，當有3間具實力的電視台提出申請，「對大部份人來說，包括我自己，都是一個令人興奮的消息」，與政府促進競爭的政策也一致，可預見將來觀眾會有更多選擇而得益。<br />\n<br />\n政府沒給公眾滿意解釋<br />\n<br />\n他指當時表現最好是港視，但政府沒接納通訊局的建議，只發兩個新免費電視牌照，港視落空，「和很多人一樣我對決定感到驚奇」。但令他更失望，是社會上有不少人提出疑問，政府都沒有給公眾一個滿意解釋，僅是以循序漸進方式引入競爭及顧問分析等作回應，「市民係睇唔到政府所作一個同佢哋期望相差咁遠嘅決定，實質理據喺邊度」，亦解釋不到為何獲發牌的兩間電視台比港視優勝。<br />\n何沛謙也重提2011年亞視誤報前國家主席江澤民死訊的風波，指當時誤報一則影響性大的新聞，且涉及是否有人蓄意繞過規管制度，在背後控制一個電視台的運作，故作為監管機構不能坐視不理。最終經過近一年調查，得出結論並公佈實情，讓公眾知道真相。事後回想過他仍覺得當時的決定合乎公眾利益。<br />\n■記者王家文"},{"pid":"a45cd5644b01f88ab17b437b91adca715834437b","tid":203060,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"已經冇人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9082fceb6c62c937556ef684925556fe551784a2","tid":203060,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經冇人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬只值得tvb一個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0f989d71b5fa7f392fcb81f3a2262a642e90715","tid":203060,"uid":50616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經冇人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬只值得tvb一個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n蛋同雞蛋問題。<br />\n<br />\n再加上 人本身就係「路徑依賴」嘅生物，要唔依賴TVB，就係要複製TVB嘅模式。（HKTV其實好明顯就係咁）<br />\n<br />\n所以香港政府唔擔心就奇怪。"},{"pid":"fe148b943a70f05b15da82bdf68f5458032c2378","tid":203060,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:40:26.000Z","msg":"對得住大律師個名<br />\n冇滿口歪理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed4c5e3f19a7c056a4242031e332a030f0c5217","tid":203060,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>已經冇人理啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n港豬只值得tvb一個台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家見viu要燒咁多錢來&quot;守&quot;<br />\n俾個牌wiki都未必肯做 <br />\n<br />\nJR完係政府身上鑿一筆捲錢走 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbe9ef01e3979aa2f0efc7ce79b0d0f8f1cb0ea","tid":203060,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"689<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}